@startuml
title LowCortisol WebApp - Shared Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Shared Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_shared_kernel_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_shared_kernel_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_shared_kernel_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_shared_kernel_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_shared_kernel_Presentation ..> Frontend_shared_kernel_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_shared_kernel_Application ..> Frontend_shared_kernel_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_shared_kernel_Application ..> Frontend_shared_kernel_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_shared_kernel_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_shared_kernel_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_shared_kernel_Presentation ..> Frontend_shared_kernel_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_shared_kernel_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/shared.
end note

@enduml
